targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  profile_picture_url
FROM "UserProfiles"
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id

SELECT
  media_count
FROM "UserInsights"
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id
ORDER BY insight_date desc
LIMIT 1

SELECT
  followers_count
FROM "UserInsights"
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id
ORDER BY insight_date DESC
LIMIT 1

SELECT
  follows_count
FROM "UserInsights"
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id
ORDER BY insight_date DESC
LIMIT 1

SELECT
  sum(like_count)
FROM "Media"
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id

SELECT
  sum(comments_count)
FROM "Media"
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id

select sum(reqSaved.totalSaved) 
from (select distinct(mi.media_id), max(mi.saved) as totalSaved
from "MediaInsights" mi, "Media" m
where saved is not null and mi.media_id = m.media_id and m.instagram_business_account = $user_id
group by mi.media_id) as reqSaved

WITH mediaCounts as (
SELECT
  sum(like_count) as likeCount,
  sum(comments_count) as commentsCount
FROM "Media"
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id
), savedCount as (
select sum(reqSaved.totalSaved) as totSaved
from (select distinct(media_id), max(saved) as totalSaved
from "MediaInsights" mi
where saved is not null
group by media_id) as reqSaved)

SELECT
  cast ((mediaCounts.likeCount + mediaCounts.commentsCount + savedCount.totSaved) as float) / followers_count as engRate
FROM "UserInsights", mediaCounts, savedCount
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id
ORDER by insight_date desc
LIMIT 1

SELECT
  media_type,
  count(media_id) as total
FROM
  "Media"
group by media_type
order by total desc

SELECT
  cast (sum(like_count) as float) / count(media_id)
FROM "Media"
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id

SELECT
  cast (sum(comments_count) as float) / count(media_id)
FROM "Media"
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id

select cast (sum(reqSaved.totalSaved) as float) / count(reqSaved.totalMedia)
from (select distinct(mi.media_id), max(mi.saved) as totalSaved, count(m.media_id) as totalMedia
from "MediaInsights" mi, "Media" m
where saved is not null and mi.media_id = m.media_id and m.instagram_business_account = $user_id
group by mi.media_id) as reqSaved

WITH engTotal as (
select sum(engAll) as eng
from (
	select max(engagement) as engAll
	from "MediaInsights" mi
	where mi.media_id in (select media_id from "Media" order by "timestamp" desc limit 20)
	group by mi.media_id 
	) as engList
)

SELECT
  cast (engTotal.eng as float) / followers_count as engRate
FROM "UserInsights", engTotal
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id
ORDER by insight_date desc
LIMIT 1

with gainsData as (select
	ui.insight_date::date,
	ui.followers_count, ui.followers_count - lag(ui.followers_count, 1) over() as followerGain,
	ui.follows_count, ui.follows_count - lag(ui.follows_count, 1) over() as followsGain,
	ui.media_count, ui.media_count - lag(ui.media_count, 1) over() as mediaGain
from "UserInsights" ui 
where ui.insight_date in (
  	select max(ui.insight_date) as lastInsight
  	from "UserInsights" ui
  	where extract(epoch from ui.insight_date)*1000 > $__from - 86400000
  	group by ui.insight_date::date
  )
  and extract(epoch from ui.insight_date)*1000 > $__from - 86400000
)

select 
  $__time(insight_date),
  followers_count, followerGain,
  follows_count, followsGain,
  media_count, mediaGain
from
  gainsData
where $__timeFilter(insight_date)
order by insight_date desc

with gainsData as (select
	ui.insight_date::date,
	ui.followers_count, ui.followers_count - lag(ui.followers_count, 1) over() as followerGain,
	ui.follows_count, ui.follows_count - lag(ui.follows_count, 1) over() as followsGain,
	ui.media_count, ui.media_count - lag(ui.media_count, 1) over() as mediaGain
from "UserInsights" ui 
where ui.insight_date in (
  	select max(ui.insight_date) as lastInsight
  	from "UserInsights" ui
  	where extract(epoch from ui.insight_date)*1000 > $__from - 86400000
  	group by ui.insight_date::date
  )
  and extract(epoch from ui.insight_date)*1000 > $__from - 86400000
)

select 
  $__time(insight_date),
  followerGain,
  followsGain,
  mediaGain
from
  gainsData
where $__timeFilter(insight_date)

with gainsData as (select
  ui.insight_date::date,
	udi.follower_count as newFollowers,
	ui.followers_count - lag(ui.followers_count, 1) over () as gainFollowers,
	udi.follower_count - (ui.followers_count - lag(ui.followers_count, 1) over ()) as lostFollowers
from "UserInsights" ui 
left join "UserDetailedInsights" udi on 
  ui.insight_date::date = udi.insight_date::date and 
  ui.instagram_business_account=udi.instagram_business_account
where 
  ui.instagram_business_account = $user_id and
  udi.follower_count is not null and
  ui.insight_date in (
  	select max(ui.insight_date) as lastInsight
  	from "UserInsights" ui
  	where ui.instagram_business_account = $user_id
  	group by ui.insight_date::date
  )
  and extract(epoch from ui.insight_date)*1000 > $__from - 86400000
)

select 
  $__time(insight_date),
  newFollowers,
  gainFollowers,
  lostFollowers
from gainsData
where $__timeFilter(insight_date)

SELECT
  insight_date AS "time",
  followers_count
FROM "UserInsights"
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(insight_date)
  and instagram_business_account = $user_id
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  insight_date AS "time",
  likes_count
FROM "UserInsights"
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(insight_date)
  and instagram_business_account = $user_id

SELECT
  insight_date AS "time",

FROM "UserInsights"
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(insight_date)
ORDER BY 1

SELECT

SELECT

SELECT

SELECT

SELECT

SELECT
